WEBVTT

00:02.965 --> 00:05.566
And The Turkish Tornado!
Make it a hat trick. Shooting!

00:05.633 --> 00:07.134
Oh, nice save!

00:07.202 --> 00:09.222
Turkish Tornado.
That's... I like that.

00:09.342 --> 00:13.474
- Hold on a second.
- What's going on? You all right?

00:13.541 --> 00:14.731
No, I thought it was Sandy.

00:14.851 --> 00:19.012
It's this gymnast that broke her leg that
we brought in. She keeps emailing me.

00:19.080 --> 00:20.480
They like a man in uniform.

00:20.547 --> 00:22.181
OK, this is her.

00:22.249 --> 00:24.357
She sent that
to you on purpose?

00:24.477 --> 00:27.012
Yeah. You know what this is?
It's 'eau de commitment", OK.

00:27.125 --> 00:28.825
I have the stink of
un-attainability on me and these

00:28.893 --> 00:30.460
women are just
coming out of the woodwork.

00:30.528 --> 00:33.463
You're a free man. I thought
Sandy left things kinda open?

00:33.531 --> 00:36.498
Well, actually, I told Sandy that I
would be here when she gets back.

00:36.566 --> 00:38.934
So I would like to be the kind
of guy that sticks to his word.

00:39.002 --> 00:41.203
Yeah, we all would, man.
I mean, but are you?

00:41.271 --> 00:44.473
Yeah, I guess I'm taking advice now
from the king of self-imposed solitude?

00:44.541 --> 00:46.341
All right. Fair enough.

00:46.409 --> 00:49.145
- You can, uh...
- Hey, guys!

00:49.212 --> 00:51.546
- Elyse.
- Hey.

00:51.613 --> 00:53.982
Toby, this is Elyse.
I trained her last year.

00:54.050 --> 00:56.151
- Really nice to meet you.
- Nice to meet you.

00:56.218 --> 00:57.518
I didn't know you guys
have a team. Do you mind?

00:57.586 --> 00:59.554
- You wanna play, yeah sure?
- Yeah, thanks.

00:59.621 --> 01:03.191
- What are you doing here?
- Rider said I should come in and set up my locker.

01:03.258 --> 01:06.260
- Thank you for leaving OZ without a partner.
- Yeah, you got my old job.

01:06.328 --> 01:09.229
- Good for you.
- I did. I'm totally stoked.

01:09.297 --> 01:10.597
Wow.

01:10.665 --> 01:12.532
- Congratulations.
- How are you? Huh?

01:12.600 --> 01:13.834
How's, uh... how's Sandy?

01:13.902 --> 01:15.869
Sandy.

01:15.937 --> 01:18.505
Sandy is in Africa.

01:18.573 --> 01:20.340
- Yes.
- She's in Africa?

01:20.408 --> 01:22.209
- Yeah.
- No way! That's amazing.

01:22.276 --> 01:25.344
Yes. Mrs. Africa.

01:25.412 --> 01:28.047
So, uh...
you wanna play?

01:28.115 --> 01:29.415
Uh.

01:29.482 --> 01:31.350
Go ahead. Could be fun.

01:31.418 --> 01:32.952
You know, actually,
we should get back to work.

01:33.020 --> 01:35.154
Yeah. That's enough kidding
around for one day, guys. OK.

01:35.222 --> 01:38.124
- Really?
- Yeah. I mean, you know it's a... it's a...

01:38.192 --> 01:41.626
Careful about that. It's just
been a lot of goofing around.

01:41.694 --> 01:43.895
- Does he want to play?
- Nah, he's gotta come with me.

01:43.963 --> 01:47.733
So we gotta get back to work, guys.
C'mon! Time. People to save.

